ody":"I think that, instead, you might want to set `wrap_in_directory: bin` in your archive settings (and set the bindir on nfpm config)...","author_association":"MEMBER","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/goreleaser/goreleaser/issues/comments/918403455/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"caarlos0","id":245435,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI0NTQzNQ==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/245435?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0","html_url":"https://github.com/caarlos0","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/goreleaser/goreleaser/issues/comments/918555871","html_url":"https://github.com/goreleaser/goreleaser/issues/2476#issuecomment-918555871","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/goreleaser/goreleaser/issues/2476","id":918555871,"node_id":"IC_kwDOBJgEXs42wAzf","user":{"login":"gssbzn","id":461027,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQ2MTAyNw==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/461027?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/gssbzn","html_url":"https://github.com/gssbzn","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gssbzn/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gssbzn/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gssbzn/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gssbzn/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gssbzn/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gssbzn/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gssbzn/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gssbzn/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gssbzn/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2021-09-13T20:36:16Z","updated_at":"2021-09-13T20:36:16Z","body":"Tried\r\n```yml\r\nbefore:\r\n  hooks:\r\n    - go mod tidy\r\n\r\nbuilds:\r\n  - <<: &build_defaults\r\n      env:\r\n        - CGO_ENABLED=0\r\n      binary: mongocli\r\n      main: ./cmd/mongocli/mongocli.go\r\n      ldflags:\r\n        - -s -w -X github.com/mongodb/mongocli/internal/version.Version={{.Version}} -X github.com/mongodb/mongocli/internal/version.GitCommit={{.FullCommit}}\r\n    id: macos\r\n    goos: [darwin]\r\n    goarch: [amd64,arm64]\r\n  - <<: *build_defaults\r\n    id: linux\r\n    goos: [linux]\r\n    goarch: [amd64,arm64]\r\n  - <<: *build_defaults\r\n    id: windows\r\n    goos: [windows]\r\n    goarch: [amd64]\r\narchives:\r\n- id: linux\r\n  builds: [linux]\r\n  <<: &archive_defaults\r\n    files:\r\n      - README.md\r\n      - LICENSE\r\n      - third_party_notices/**/*\r\n    replacements:\r\n      darwin: macos\r\n      amd64: x86_64\r\n    wrap_in_directory: bin\r\n  format: tar.gz\r\n- id: macos\r\n  builds: [macos]\r\n  <<: *archive_defaults\r\n  format: zip\r\n- id: windows\r\n  builds: [windows]\r\n  <<: *archive_defaults\r\n  format: zip\r\nnfpms:\r\n- package_name: mongocli\r\n  vendor: MongoDB Inc.\r\n  homepage: https://www.mongodb.com/\r\n  maintainer: MongoDB Inc. <support@mongodb.com>\r\n  description: MongoDB Command Line Interface (mongocli) is a tool for managing your MongoDB cloud services, like MongoDB Atlas, MongoDB Cloud Manager, and MongoDB Ops Manager.\r\n  license: Apache 2.0\r\n  bindir: /usr/bin\r\n  builds: [linux]\r\n  formats: [deb,rpm]\r\n  replacements:\r\n    amd64: x86_64\r\nchecksum:\r\n  name_template: checksums.txt\r\nsnapshot:\r\n  name_template: \"{{ .Version }}-next\"\r\nchangelog:\r\n  sort: asc\r\n  filters:\r\n    exclude:\r\n    - '^docs:'\r\n    - '^test:'\r\n    - '^task:'\r\n    - '^build(deps):'\r\nrelease:\r\n  prerelease: auto\r\n  name_template: \"MongoDB CLI {{.Version}}\"\r\n  extra_files:\r\n    - glob: ./bin/*.msi\r\n```\r\n\r\nthat wraps all the files, we end up with the binary, `mongocli`, README and LICENSE files all under `bin`, we like our current structure, `bin/mongocli` and README and LICENSE at the top level\r\n\r\nAnd to be clear I'm not saying there's a bug but the behaviour has been changing back and forth and I'd like some clarification here, the first time caught us by surprise, at least now we have a set of tests to make sure the RPM and DEB packages work as expected and how I came here to confirm the behaviour ","author_association":"NONE","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/goreleaser/goreleaser/issues/comments/918555871/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"gssbzn","id":461027,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQ2MTAyNw==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/461027?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/gssbzn","html_url":"https://github.com/gssbzn","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gssbzn/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gssbzn/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gssbzn/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gssbzn/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gssbzn/subscriptions","organizations_